\n| note11 = [[Mantronix]] Remix\n| writer11 = {{hlist|D. Armstrong|R. Armstrong|Nowels}}\n| extra11 = {{hlist|Dido|Rollo|[[Kurtis Mantronik]]{{ref|b|[b]}}{{ref|c|[c]}}}}\n| length11 = 4:31\n\n| title12 = Blackbird\n| note12 = [[Moguai]] Remix\n| writer12 = {{hlist|D. Armstrong|R. Armstrong}}\n| extra12 = {{hlist|Dido|Rollo|[[Moguai|Andr\u00e9 Tegeler]]{{ref|b|[b]}}{{ref|c|[c]}}}}\n| length12 = 6:46\n\n| title13 = Northern Skies\n| note13 = Rollo Remix\n| writer13 = {{hlist|D. Armstrong|R. Armstrong}}\n| extra13 = {{hlist|Dido|The Ark|Brion|Rollo{{ref|b|[b]}}}}\n| length13 = 5:53}}\n\n;Notes\n*{{sup|{{note|a|[a]}}}} signifies a co-producer\n*{{sup|{{note|b|[b]}}}} signifies a remixer\n*{{sup|{{note|c|[c]}}}} signifies an additional producer\n\n==Chart performance==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2013)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br/>position\n|-\n|[[ARIA Charts|Australian ARIA Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"ARIA Report 1240\">[http://pandora.nla.gov.au/pan/23790/20131216-1442/Issue%201240.pdf] ARIA Report 1240. December 2, 2013</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|96\n|-\n{{albumchart|Flanders|81|artist=Dido|album=Greatest Hits}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Wallonia|61|artist=Dido|album=Greatest Hits}}\n|-\n|China Albums Chart [[Sino Chart]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sino-chart.com/chart/overall.html |title=Sino-Chart \u4fe1\u8bfa\u699c (\u7efc\u5408\u699c) |publisher=Sino-Chart.com |accessdate=27 April 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6VdhSFeJi?url=http://www.sino-chart.com/chart/overall.html |archivedate=17 January 2015 }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18\n|-\n|Croatian International Albums Chart <ref>http://www.hdu-toplista.com/download.php?what=pdf_lista&id=1326</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|11\n|-\n{{albumchart|Ireland|41|year=2013|week=48}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Scottish Albums Chart<ref>[http://www.officialcharts.com/charts/scottish-albums-chart/20131201/40 Official Scottish Albums Chart Top 100 