erry Groves|Groves]]\n|location   = [[Birmingham]]\n|stadium    = [[Villa Park]]\n|attendance = 32,486\n|referee    = \n|result     = W\n|stack      = yes\n}}\n{{Footballbox collapsible\n|date       = 2 January 1989\n|round      = 19\n|time       = \n|team1      = [[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]\n|score      = 2\u20130\n|report     = \n|team2      = [[Tottenham Hotspur F.C.|Tottenham Hotspur]]\n|goals1     = Merson {{goal}} <br> Thomas {{goal}}\n|goals2     = \n|location   = [[London]]\n|stadium    = [[Arsenal Stadium|Highbury]]\n|attendance = 45,129\n|referee    = \n|result     = W\n|stack      = yes\n}}\n{{Footballbox collapsible\n|date       = 14 January 1989\n|round      = 20\n|time       = \n|team1      = [[Everton F.C.|Everton]]\n|score      = 1\u20133\n|report     = \n|team2      = [[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]\n|goals1     = \n|goals2     = {{goal}} Merson <br> {{goal}} Smith <br> {{goal}} [[Kevin Richardson (footballer)|Richardson]]\n|location   = [[Liverpool]]\n|stadium    = [[Goodison Park]]\n|attendance = 34,825\n|referee    = \n|result     = W\n|stack      = yes\n}}\n{{Footballbox collapsible\n|date       = 21 January 1989\n|round      = 21\n|time       = \n|team1      = [[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]\n|score      = 1\u20131\n|report     = \n|team2      = [[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|Sheffield Wednesday]]\n|goals1     = Merson {{goal}}\n|goals2     = \n|location   = [[London]]\n|stadium    = [[Arsenal Stadium|Highbury]]\n|attendance = 33,490\n|referee    = \n|result     = D\n|stack      = yes\n}}\n{{Footballbox collapsible\n|date       = 4 February 1989\n|round      = 22\n|time       = \n|team1      = [[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]\n|score      = 2\u20131\n|report     = \n|team2      = [[West Ham United F.C.|West Ham United]]\n|goals1     = Smith {{goal}} <br> Groves {{goal}}\n|goals2     = \n|location   = [[London]]\n|stadium    = [[Arsenal Stadium|Highbury]]\n|attendance = 40,139\n|referee    = \n|result     = W\n|stack      = yes\n}}\n{{Footballbox collapsible\n|date       = 